<HEADLINE>
<P>
LEONA HELMSLEY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Leona Helmsley was correct when she said, "Only the little people pay taxes." 
Her big mistake was in bragging about it! 
</P>
<P>
Her conviction will probably not result in an all-out assault on the many other 
tycoons who cheat the IRS. But it will remind them not to be so arrogant and 
outspoken about it! 
</P>
<P>
CLARENCE W. HAYWARD 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
