INDUSTRY -- SAN FRANCISCO; AGNOS, ART; INDUSTRIAL EQUIPMENT; EQUIPMENT 
FAILURES; HIGH RISE BUILDINGS; INDUSTRIAL ACCIDENTS -- SAN FRANCISCO 
</P>
