FOREIGN RELATIONS -- CHINA; ROMANIA -- REVOLTS; CHINA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
ROMANIA; CHINA -- POLITICS; UNITED STATES -- TRADE -- CHINA 
</P>
