together to work with brushes and ink. NICK SOUZA / For The Times; Photo, 
Classes over, Alex Chen, 8, of Irvine is ready for a ride home from his mother. 
The Chinese school meets Sundays from 9 a.m. to noon. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
